posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'Luxury comes standard at Carrington Oaks, where our one, two, and three bedroom apartments provide the home base you’ve been looking for in Buda, TX.', 'In each apartment, you will appreciate finer details like stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and a garden-style soaking tub that enhance the ambiance of your home.', 'Community amenities include a lounge with a fireplace and billiards, a resort-style swimming pool with fountains, and a business center for getting work done from home.', 'Embrace a luxury lifestyle at Carrington Oaks.', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'October 1, 2022', 'Pets:', 'Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes:', '•Pet Deposits $250/pet•Pet Fees: $250/pet•$25 Pet Rent/Pet•2 Pet Max•80 lb Weight Limit', 'Deposit:', 'Leasing options:', '3 months,6 months,9 months,9+ months,12 months,12+ months', 'Leasing notes:', 'Application fee:', '$55 Application Fee & $150 Administration Fee', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'Utilities Cost:', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Parking type:', 'Garage, Covered, Off-Street', 'Parking notes:', 'Appliances:', 'Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Garbage disposal, Microwave, Range/Oven', 'Exterior:', 'Private pool, Balcony/patio, Yard-Fenced', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Air conditioning, Ceiling fans', 'Wiring:', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Shared pool, Fitness center, Clubhouse, Playground, Barbecue, Theater', 'Security and Access:', 'Controlled access', 'Views:', 'City, Surrounding Business, Courtyard', 'Additional features:', 'Hardwood floor, Granite countertop', 'Offered by:', 'Carrington Oaks', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
